Long       Gryan Stoutmantle stands tall atop Sentinel Hill, watching the horizon.
~
Desc       The stalwart leader of the People's Militia. Disillusioned by Stormwind's
failure to protect Westfall, Gryan has organized the local farmers into a
fighting force to take back their homes from the Defias Brotherhood.
~
