#ROOM
Vnum     12519
Name     &OJangolode Mine - Entrance&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A large, gaping hole in the earth marks the entrance to the Jangolode
Mine. Defias Trappers guard the entrance, ensuring their illicit mining
operations are not disturbed.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12518
Desc      The western plains.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12520
Desc      Descend into the mine.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12504 1 12519
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12520
Name     &dJangolode Mine - Depths&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The air in the mine is thick with dust and the sounds of pickaxes.
The Defias are stripping the mine bare of copper and tin to fund
VanCleef's war machine.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12519
Desc      The surface.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12521
Name     &CThe Gold Coast&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The dusty plains finally give way to the sandy shores of the Great Sea.
The water is cool and inviting, but the beach is crawling with vicious,
gurgling murlocs who violently defend their territory.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12518
Desc      The Dust Plains.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12525
Desc      The Long Shore.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12522
Desc      A clustered murloc camp.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12513 2 12521
  Reset E 1 12508 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12522
Name     &CThe Gold Coast - Murloc Camp&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Crude huts made of driftwood and seaweed are clustered here. The smell
of rotting fish is overwhelming. Murloc Coastrunners charge at you with
jagged spears the moment you are spotted.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12521
Desc      The Gold Coast.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12523
Desc      The shallow waters of the sea.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12513 2 12522
  Reset G 1 12507 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12523
Name     &CThe Gold Coast - Shallow Waters&d~
Sector   water_noswim~
Desc     You are wading in the cool, salty waters of the Great Sea. To the south,
the massive, rusted hull of a shipwreck juts out of the water, a stark
reminder of the treacherous reefs along this coast.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12522
Desc      The murloc camp on the beach.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12524
Desc      The shipwreck.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12524
Name     &CThe Shipwreck&d~
Sector   water_noswim~
Desc     The ruined hull of a merchant vessel provides a perfect lair for the
terror of the Gold Coast. Old Murk-Eye, a massive and unusually intelligent
murloc, claims this wreck as his throne.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12523
Desc      The shallow waters.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12514 1 12524
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12525
Name     &CThe Long Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The beach stretches out to the north. In the distance, rising high above
the rocky cliffs, you can see the flashing beacon of the Westfall
Lighthouse, warning ships away from the deadly shore.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12521
Desc      The Gold Coast.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12526
Desc      The base of the lighthouse.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12526
Name     &OWestfall Lighthouse - Base&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The lighthouse is built on a high, rocky promontory overlooking the sea.
The structure is old but sturdy. A heavy wooden door at the base leads
up to the beacon.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12525
Desc      The Long Shore.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12527
Desc      Climb the lighthouse stairs.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12527
Name     &OWestfall Lighthouse - Top&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive, oil-burning beacon illuminates the room, casting sweeping
beams of light out over the ocean. The spectral form of Captain Grayson,
the Keeper of the Flame, stands here, eternally bound to his duty.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12526
Desc      The base of the lighthouse.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12515 1 12527
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12528
Name     &OThe Dust Plains - East&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The plains on the eastern side of Westfall are infested with scavengers.
The scent of wet dog and decaying meat signals your approach to a major
encampment of Riverpaw Gnolls.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12506
Desc      The plains south of Furlbrow's.
~
#ENDEXIT
