Sector   field~
Desc     A chaotic, filthy camp filled with crude hide tents and gnawed bones.
Packs of Riverpaw Gnolls bicker and fight among themselves, only uniting
when an intruder stumbles into their territory.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12528
Desc      The eastern plains.
~
#ENDEXIT
